{
  "stem": "8359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the girls dealt with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shaved their heads, beat them up, maybe killed one or two.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was retaliation, definitely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took me a week on the cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the-- it was chaos-- chaos-- traveling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they gave us some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] I think they gave us some.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went back to Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, they had already established a-- a committee, a Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because, I-- well, first of all, I was liberated a day later than anybody else, which wasn't really that much of a difference.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did I find?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to my home, my apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, by Pollocks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Hitler didn't kill you yet?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the reaction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler didn't kill you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew I'm not going to live there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went together, a few girls that we-- you know, a group that we stuck together over the years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know how we got an apartment, a room, or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we moved in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't even know how we lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe we got money from the committee, the Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so I came into this committee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I registered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to know, did anybody-- stop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About six weeks-- between four and six weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a whole bunch of us picked ourselves up and, ironically, went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because all the action was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
